properties.NAME: CENTRAL DELTA AGGREGATE AREA
properties.Description: There are three regions included in this model labeled "Delta Aggregate Area" that are aggregations of smaller areas throughout the North, Central and South Deltas. They are included so that the model area encompasses all land within the legally defined Sacramento-San Joaquin River Delta.
